<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Recipe to craft these: 1 Celestial Essence, Sculpting tools, 1 Large Block of Magic Clay, 1 Laquered Opal, 1 Ceramic Lining Sketch. Combine this part in Pottery Wheel. That yields 1 unfired opal encrusted stein. Then, 1 unfired opal encrusted stein, 1 High Quality Firing Sheet, Fire in Kiln = Opal Encrusted Stein.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
