		   <span class="sm">Posted: Apr 20th  2003 at  6:16am EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=12035;mid=105083148178955#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=220999"><span class="Scholar">tinamou</span></a><b><span class="Scholar"><br/>Scholar</span></b>
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Default  </span><br />
<br/><a href="/db/item.html?item=12035;page=1;howmany=50#105083148178955"><img alt="" title="Use this to create a link to this post" src="/shared/garrowrt.png" border="0" height="9" width="11" /> Link to this post</a>
<br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td>
<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Hey Folks, <br /> <br />This is what I found out. I am a druid and I know that druids can sneak. I don't know about other classes. <br />First of all buy 2 of these thingies in the bazaar. As everyone knows the bazaar started a major price drop. Now you can buy these for 20pp per piece. <br />Then go to a vendor, preferably in the city where you started out inthe beginning cos down there you're an ally. Cos what the NPC cons to you is important for the price. <br />Take off your weapon and hold 1 Opal in the primary and 1 in the secondary. Then stand behind the NPC (or the sneak thing won't work), then hit sneak ...and start selling or buying. <br />The price difference is great. It can be up to 20%. <br />In that way you can buy cheaper and sell with a higher return. <br />Try it out. sell : <br />1 - in front, not holding the opals <br />2 - in front holding the opals <br />3 - back, sneak, not holding the opals <br />4 - back, sneak, holding opals <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><em class="fs8">Edited, Sun Apr 20 05:41:32 2003</em></p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Skodax-Druid-E'CI Server</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td><td align="right" class="fs8" >1 reply</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
