<p>Your sneak method is well described, but Druids dont get sneak. I am guessing youre a halfling, and as an innate ability, they get sneak, as well as hide. These two dont over their skill cap of 50, so it might take a few tries to sneak successfully behind a vendor and have them con indifferently to you.Other that that, great strategy.</p>
