<p>Well first she's a halfling, not a dwarf... the hairy feet should tip you off! <br /> <br />And second, she has absolutley NO permanent inventory, all she ever sells is stuff sold to her by players.  If you ever click on her right after a patch or server reset, you'll notice her inventory is completely empty. <br /> <br />Most likely (especially since there's a pottery wheel and kiln not too far from where she stands) some player was making steins for pottry practice and just didn't feel like taking the time to sell these to players, so dumped them off on her. <br /> <br /><em class="fs8">Edited, Fri Nov 15 10:24:45 2002</em></p>
